| Role | Verbs | Frame |
|------|-------|-------|
| **Startup / SaaS** | Owned, Built, Shipped | Ownership + speed + breadth |
| **SRE** | Sustained, Drove, Authored, Eliminated | SLOs/MTTR/toil/error budgets/runbooks/on-call |
| **Cloud Engineer** | Architected, Designed, Operated, Provisioned | AWS service depth + architecture + cost |
| **DevOps Engineer** | Designed, Automated, Provisioned, Maintained | Pipeline volume + automation + uptime |
